    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei salvatoris Iesu Christi. Nos <persName key="#Princeps"
                            ref="#people/4105">Gisolfus</persName> divina providentia Longobardorum
                        gentis princeps pro amore Dei et Beate Marie semper virgini, cuius
                        patrocinio subsistimus et regnamus, et pro salute anime nostre seu patrie
                        nostre, concedimus et in perpetuum confirmamus dompno <persName
                            key="#Archbishops" ref="#people/4153">Amato</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabili</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/84" key="#Cities">Salernitano</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Archbishops">archiepiscopo</rs> et successoribus suis atque <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs><orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2326"
                            key="#Mother_churches"> Sancte Dei genitricis et Virginis Marie et Beati
                            Mathei apostoli et evangeliste</orgName>, in qua prefatus dompnus Amatus
                        regimen tenere videtur, hec omnia subscripta que ad ipsa ecclesia iuste
                        novimus pertinere, videlicet: <rs key="#Casalia">casale</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/4728"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Cusentinorum</placeName> cum omnibus hominibus et tenimentis suis,
                        tenimenta <placeName ref="#places/4729"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Fisheries #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Ports"
                            >Dolacarie</placeName> et <placeName ref="#places/4730"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Fisheries #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Ports"
                            >Pressani</placeName>que sunt ultra ripam <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >fluminis</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Rivers" ref="#places/4731">Sileris</placeName> et <rs
                            key="#Ports">portum</rs>
                        <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">cannicias</rs> et <rs key="#Fisheries"
                            >piscationes</rs> ipsius <rs key="#Rivers">fluminis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">tenimenta</rs> cum <rs key="#Forests"
                            >silvis</rs> Pecte, <rs key="#Casalia">casale</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/4726"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Liciniani</placeName>, <rs key="#Casalia #Walls">castrum</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/4725"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Rivers #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Mills #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Walls"
                            >Olibani</placeName> cum omnibus hominibus et bonis eorum habitantes et
                        abitaturos in ipso et pertinenciis eius et cum omnibus iuribus, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs key="#Rivers">aquis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Mills">molinis</rs> et tenimentis suis; concedimus etiam ipsi
                        ecclesie Salernitane <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Coloni/tenants #Slave_labour #Agricultural_workers #Freeborn #Slave"
                            ref="#places/4732">casale Sancti Victoris de Gifone</placeName> et
                            <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Casalia #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Coloni/tenants #Slave_labour #Agricultural_workers #Freeborn #Slave"
                            ref="#places/3466">casale de Scalcinati </placeName>cum omnibus
                        hominibus et terris ipsorum et omnes homines ipsius ecclesie ubicumque
                        fuerint <rs key="#Freeborn">liberi</rs>, <rs key="#Slave">servi</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Coloni/tenants #Slave_labour #Agricultural_workers">censiles
                            rusticos vel stauriti</rs> et eorum <rs
                            key="#Privileges #Immunity #Exemption">liberi ab omni collecta et
                            publicis serviciis sint immunes</rs> [e]t ut liceat prefato dompno Amato
                        archiepiscopo et successoribus suis omni tempore homines undecumque et
                        quandocumque venerint recipere et tenere tam in hac nostra civitate Salerni
                        quam et in quibuscumque loca Salernitane diocesis et provincie sue, et coram
                        eo et suis successoribus de omnes civiles questiones conveniri debeant et a
                        suo iudice iudicari. Et ut hec omnia in perpetuum observentur, hoc roboreum
                        preceptum concessionis et confirmationis ex iussione supradicte potestatis
                        scripsi ego <persName key="#Notary" ref="#people/4151">Iohannes</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, in sacro <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/84">Salernitano</placeName> palacio, quinto anno
                        principatus ipsius domni Gisolfi principis, mense augusto, indictione
                        decima.</ab>
